Wake Up To Breaking News! SUBMIT

Okurrrrr!Cardi B brought her fabulous self and that baby bump of hers to the 2018 Met Gala red carpet tonight.The always outrageous rapper brought her flawless style to the star-studded gala, which has selected the theme of Heavenly Bodies: Fashion and the Catholic Imagination.For the fashion event of the year, the pregnant rapper opted for white pearl-encrusted ensemble, complete with matching bejeweled headdress and train, all by Moschino....
title: Cardi B Steals the Spotlight in Over-the-Top Moschino Ensemble at the 2018 Met Gala
